'''地平說'''是一種古老的[[世界觀|世界觀]]，地平说與[[地圓說|地圓說]]相對，認為[[地表|地表]]是[[平面_(数学)|平面]]，而不是一個巨大的[[球面|球面]]。这种观点是绝大多数民族古代长期持有的观点，包括[[古希腊|古希腊]]前的希腊文明，[[希腊化时代|希腊化时代]]前的[[中东|中东]]，[[笈多王朝|笈多王朝]]前的[[古印度|古印度]]和17世纪前的[[中国|中国]]<ref>Joseph Needham et al.: "Heavenly clockwork: the great astronomical clocks of medieval China", Antiquarian Horological Society, 2nd. ed., Vol. 1, 1986, {{ISBN|0-521-32276-6}}, p. 138.</ref><ref name="needham volume 3 499">Needham, Joseph (1986). Science and Civilization in China: Volume 3. Taipei: Caves Books, Ltd. p. 499.</ref>。

尽管[[地圆说|地圆说]]拥有大量科学证据<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.columbia.edu/cu/21stC/issue-3.4/macdougall.html |title=Strange enthusiasms: a brief history of American pseudoscience |first=Robert |last=MacDougall |publisher=[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]] |access-date=2016-07-05 |archive-date=2019-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190212155322/http://www.columbia.edu/cu/21stC/issue-3.4/macdougall.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author1=邹松霖 |title=如何证明地球是圆的？ |journal=中国经济周刊 |date=2019 |issue=13}}</ref>，[[伪科学|伪科学性]]的地平说[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]在[[地平說學會|现代地平說學會]]的支持下正在逐步兴起，并通过[[社会化媒体|社交媒体]]影响那些未曾了解地圆说的人群<ref name="Ambrose">{{cite news|url=http://www.denverpost.com/2017/07/07/colorado-earth-flat-gravity-hoax/|title=These Coloradans say Earth is flat. And gravity's a hoax. Now, they're being persecuted.|last1=Ambrose|first1=Graham|date=2017-07-07|work=[[丹佛邮报|The Denver Post]]|accessdate=2017-08-19|archive-date=2018-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914154115/https://www.denverpost.com/2017/07/07/colorado-earth-flat-gravity-hoax/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dure">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/jan/20/flat-earth-believers-youtube-videos-conspiracy-theorists|title=Flat-Earthers are back: 'It's almost like the beginning of a new religion'|last1=Dure|first1=Beau|date=2016-01-20|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2017-08-19|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827132052/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2016/jan/20/flat-earth-believers-youtube-videos-conspiracy-theorists|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

地圆说起源于公元前6世纪的[[毕达哥拉斯|毕达哥拉斯]]时期的希腊哲学，尽管大多数前苏格拉底主义者直到公元前5世纪都认为地球是平的。公元前4世纪初，[[柏拉图|柏拉图]]将地圆说写入著作，公元前330年，他的学生亚里士多德以经验为依据提供了地球球形的证据。从这时起，地圆说开始被世界所接受<ref>Continuation of Greek concept into Roman and medieval Christian thought: Reinhard Krüger: ''[http://www.uni-stuttgart.de/lettres/krueger/forschungsvorhaben_erdkugeltheorie_biblio.html Materialien und Dokumente zur mittelalterlichen Erdkugeltheorie von der Spätantike bis zur Kolumbusfahrt (1492)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.uni-stuttgart.de/lettres/krueger/forschungsvorhaben_erdkugeltheorie_biblio.html |date=20070704120620 }}''</ref><ref>Direct adoption of the Greek concept by Islam: Ragep, F. Jamil: "Astronomy", in: Krämer, Gudrun (ed.) et al.: ''Encyclopaedia of Islam'', THREE, Brill 2010, without page numbers</ref><ref>Direct adoption by India: [[David_Pingree|D. Pingree]]: "History of Mathematical Astronomy in India", ''Dictionary of Scientific Biography'', Vol. 15 (1978), pp. 533–633 (554ff.); Glick, Thomas F., Livesey, Steven John, Wallis, Faith (eds.): "Medieval Science, Technology, and Medicine: An Encyclopedia", Routledge, New York 2005, {{ISBN|0-415-96930-1}}, p. 463</ref><ref>Adoption by China via European science: Jean-Claude Martzloff, [http://www.eastm.org/index.php/journal/article/viewFile/526/457 "Space and Time in Chinese Texts of Astronomy and of Mathematical Astronomy in the Seventeenth and Eighteenth Centuries"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eastm.org/index.php/journal/article/viewFile/526/457 |date=20190907183516 }}, ''Chinese Science'' 11 (1993–94): 66–92 (69) and Christopher Cullen, "A Chinese Eratosthenes of the Flat Earth: A Study of a Fragment of Cosmology in Huai Nan tzu 淮 南 子", ''Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies'', Vol. 39, No. 1 (1976), pp. 106–27 (107)</ref>。

== 历史 ==
=== 地平说的旧传播时代 ===
==== 西亚 ====
在早期[[埃及神话|埃及]]<ref>H. and H. A. Frankfort, J. A. Wilson, and T. Jacobsen, Before Philosophy (Baltimore: Penguin, 1949) 54.</ref>和{{tsl|en|Mesopotamian_myths|美索不达米亚神话|美索不达米亚}}观念中，世界被描述成一个漂浮在海洋上的大盘子。前8世纪[[荷马时代|荷马时代]]的神话也有类似的描述：“阿诺斯，祂水一般的身躯环绕着大地的圆弧面，是所有生命和神明的起源。”<ref>{{Cite book|title=The Dream of Reason|last=Gottlieb|first=Anthony|date=2000|publisher=Penguin|isbn=978-0-393-04951-0|location=|page=[https://archive.org/details/dreamofreasonhis00anth/page/6 6]|url=https://archive.org/details/dreamofreasonhis00anth/page/6}}</ref>

古埃及的{{tsl|en|Pyramid Texts|金字塔文}}和{{tsl|en|Coffin Texts|棺椁文}}也有类似的世界观。在他们的世界观中[[努恩_(古埃及)|努恩]] （海洋之神）环绕着“nbwt” (“干燥的大地”或者说“群岛”）<ref>''Pyramid Texts'', Utterance 366, 629a–29c: "Behold, thou art great and round like the Great Round; Behold, thou are bent around, and art round like the Circle which encircles the nbwt; Behold, thou art round and great like the Great Circle which sets."''(Faulkner 1969, 120)''</ref><ref>''Ancient Near Eastern Texts'', Pritchard, 1969, p. 374.</ref><ref>''Coffin Texts'', Spell 714.</ref>。
==== 欧洲 ====
<!--need update as ancient-->
直到古希臘時代，约前4世紀，许多古希腊学者开始利用[[科学|科学]]（而不是基于[[宗教|宗教]]或者[[神话|神话]]）讨论地球形狀。後来，[[亚里士多德|亚里士多德]]总结了3种方法来证明大地是球形的：

* 越往北走，[[北极星|北极星]]越高；越往南走，北极星越低，且可以看到一些在北方看不到的新的星星。
* 远航的船只，先露出桅杆顶，慢慢露出船身，最后才看得到整艘船。
* 在[[月食|月食]]的时候，地球投到月球上的形状为圆形。

[[埃拉托斯特尼|埃拉托斯特尼]]第一个提出公式计算了地球的半径，尽管由于当时的观测精度有限，其结果与今日之观测相差甚大。

中世纪时，[[罗马教会|罗马教会]]将基於地圓說所建立的[[地心说|地心说]]奉为正统。最後到[[地理大發現|地理大發現時代]][[麥哲倫|麥哲倫]]所率領的船隊繞地球一周被认为直接证明了地圆说。

==== 中国 ====
{{main|中国天文学史}}

[[中国历史|中國古人]]长期讨论地圆或地平，最早的人们普遍认同天圆地方的早期[[蓋天說|蓋天說]]<ref name="needham volume 3 498">Needham, Joseph (1986). Science and Civilization in China: Volume 3. Taipei: Caves Books, Ltd. p. 498.</ref>。<!--致以后的编者，英文维基认为中国古代一直认同天圆地方这种理论其实不完全对，见[[盖天说|盖天说]]、[[浑天说|浑天说]]和[[宣天说|宣天说]]-->这种理论与后来的[[浑天说|浑天说]]有着长期的争论，不过受众依然很广<ref name="Jean-Claude Martzloff 69">{{cite journal |last=Martzloff |first=Jean-Claude |date=1993–94 |title=Space and Time in Chinese Texts of Astronomy and of Mathematical Astronomy in the Seventeenth and Eighteenth Centuries |url=http://www.eastm.org/index.php/journal/article/viewFile/526/457 |journal=Chinese Science |volume= |issue=11 |pages=66–92 [p. 69] |jstor=43290474 |access-date=2020-05-08 |archive-date=2019-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190907183516/http://www.eastm.org/index.php/journal/article/viewFile/526/457 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Cullen |first=Christopher |date=1980 |title=Joseph Needham on Chinese Astronomy |journal=[[Past_&_Present_(journal)|Past & Present]] |volume=87 |issue=1 |pages=39–53 [pp. 42, 49] |doi=10.1093/past/87.1.39 |jstor=650565}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last=Cullen |first=Christopher |date=1976 |title=A Chinese Eratosthenes of the Flat Earth: A Study of a Fragment of Cosmology in Huai Nan tzu 淮 南 子 |journal=Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies |volume=39 |issue=1 |pages=106–27 [pp. 107–09] |doi=10.1017/S0041977X00052137}}</ref>。

=== 中世纪：地平说作为替代理论或混合理论 ===
{{Further|大地测量学史|地圆说}}
====希腊：圆形的大地====
[[File:Partial_Lunar_Eclipse_2019-07-16.jpg|thumb]]中[[月球|月球]]的半圆形阴影]]
公元前6世纪-5世纪，[[毕达哥拉斯|毕达哥拉斯]]和[[巴门尼德|巴门尼德]]分别独立的提出了[[地圆说|地球是圆的]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://archive.org/details/historyofplaneta00dreyuoft|title=A History of Astronomy from Thales to Kepler|last=Dreyer|first=John Louis Emil|date=1953|publisher=[[Dover_Publications|Dover Publications]]|isbn=978-0-486-60079-6|location=New York, NY|pages=[https://archive.org/stream/historyofplaneta00dreyuoft#page/20/mode/1up 20], [https://archive.org/stream/historyofplaneta00dreyuoft#page/37/mode/1up 37–38]|ref=Reference-Dreyer-1953|authorlink=J. L. E. Dreyer|origyear=1905}}</ref>，这种理论很快就传遍了希腊地区。公元前330年，[[亚里士多德|亚里士多德]]第一次使用基础物理学和观测证据在著作中估计了地球的{{tsl|en|Earth's circumference|地球的周长|周长}}<ref>''On the Heavens'', Book ii Chapter 14. {{Cite book |last= Lloyd |first= G.E.R. |authorlink= G. E. R. Lloyd |title= Aristotle: The Growth and Structure of His Thought |publisher= Cambridge Univ. Press |date= 1968 |pages= [https://archive.org/details/aristotlegrowths0000lloy/page/162 162–64] |isbn= 978-0-521-07049-2 |url= https://archive.org/details/aristotlegrowths0000lloy/page/162 }}</ref>。更为精准的测量来自[[埃拉托斯特尼|埃拉托斯特尼]]于公元前240年的测算<ref>{{Cite book |first= Albert |last= Van Helden |title= Measuring the Universe: Cosmic Dimensions from Aristarchus to Halley |publisher= University of Chicago Press |date= 1985 |pages= 4–5 |isbn= 978-0-226-84882-2}}</ref>。公元2世纪，[[克劳狄乌斯·托勒密|克劳狄乌斯·托勒密]]在[[地理學指南|地理學指南]]中将地球描述为一个球体，并且简单划分了[[纬度|纬度]]、[[经度|经度]]和{{tsl|en|clime|气候区}}。他的同类型著作《[[至大論|至大論]]》直到11世纪才传入阿拉伯世界。

[[卢克莱修|卢克莱修]]反对毕达哥拉斯等人的观念，因为他认为地圆说描绘的宇宙意味着宇宙不存在中心，此外，他认为南半球人们倒立走路这一观念十分荒谬<ref>{{Cite book|title=Lucretius and the Transformation of Greek Wisdom|last=Sedley|first=David N.|date=2003|publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn=978-0-521-54214-2|place=Cambridge|pages=78–82|ref=harv}}</ref><ref>Lucretius, ''De rerum natura'', 1.1052–82.</ref>。公元1世纪，[[老普林尼|老普林尼]]公开宣称所有人都应该相信地球是圆的<ref>''[[博物志_(老普林尼)|Natural History]]'', 2.64</ref>，不过在这一时期地圆说依然无法解释许多问题：例如映体的性质以及如何将[[洋|洋]]保持为弯曲形状，这一时期相关的争论仍在继续。

====南亚====
[[Image:Offshore_windpark_Thorntonbank.jpg|thumb]]的照片中，更远的塔楼的下部越来越被地平线所掩盖，证明了地球的[[曲率|曲率]]]]
[[吠陀|吠陀]]的经文以多种方式描绘了宇宙<ref>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=auqGWz2l9pYC&pg=PA47 |title=The Vedic Origins of Karma: Cosmos as Man in Ancient Indian Myth and Ritual |last=Tull |first=Herman Wayne |publisher=[[纽约州立大学|State University of New York Press]] |year=1989 |isbn=978-0-7914-0094-4 |pages=47–49 |quote=The Vedic texts contain several depictions of the shape of the cosmos. The Rigveda alone contains two basic images of the cosmos: a bipartite cosmos, consisting of the two spheres of heavens and Earth, and a tripartite cosmos consisting of the three spheres of heavens and Earth (...) |access-date=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823150710/https://books.google.com/books?id=auqGWz2l9pYC&pg=PA47 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Selin2013p114">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GzjpCAAAQBAJ |title=Encyclopaedia of the History of Science, Technology, and Medicine in Non-Westen Cultures |last=Sarma |first=K. V. |publisher=Springer Science & Business Media |year=2013 |isbn=978-94-017-1416-7 |editor=Selin |editor-first=Helaine |pages=114–15 |access-date=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823150716/https://books.google.com/books?id=GzjpCAAAQBAJ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。印度最早的宇宙学著作之一将地球描述为一堆扁平磁盘{{sfn|Plofker|2009|p=52}}。

在吠陀的经文中，将[[特尤斯|特尤斯]]（天空）和[[頗哩提毗|頗哩提毗]]（大地）与[[軸|车轴]]上的车轮进行比较，得出了扁平模型<ref name="Gombrich">{{cite book |url=https://archive.org/details/ancientcosmologi0000unse/page/110 |title=Ancient Cosmologies |last=Gombrich |first=R. F. |publisher=George Allen & Unwin |year=1975 |isbn=9780041000382 |editor1=Blacker |editor-first=Carmen |pages=[https://archive.org/details/ancientcosmologi0000unse/page/110 110–39] |editor2=Loewe |editor-first2=Michael |dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞瑟·安東尼·麥克唐在著作中认为，“地球是一个被海洋包围的圆盘的概念并没有直接的在《梵书》中出现，但是人们自然而然地认为就是这样的，并将其与轮子比较（10.89），并且在之后的《百道梵書》中详细描绘了这一点<ref>{{cite book |author=A. A. Macdonell |title=Vedic Mythology |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=b7Meabtj8mcC&pg=PA9 |year=1986 |publisher=Motilal Banarsidass |isbn=978-81-208-1113-3 |page=9 |access-date=2020-08-12 |archive-date=2020-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200823150721/https://books.google.com/books?id=b7Meabtj8mcC&pg=PA9 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。”

==现代地平说==
{{Main|地平说学会}}
即便是到了现代，多个知名团体与个人仍表达了对地平的[[伪科学|伪科学性]]信仰。
===互联网时代为地平说带来的复兴===
<!-- 本部分内容部分共识来源于英文维基百科，在中文维基百科并未达成共识-->
在[[信息时代|信息时代]]，如[[YouTube|YouTube]]<ref name="YouTube converted people">{{cite news |title=How YouTube converted people to flat Earth |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/av/stories-49021903/flat-earth-how-did-youtube-help-spread-a-conspiracy-theory |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=BBC News |language=en |archive-date=2020-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612135528/https://www.bbc.com/news/av/stories-49021903/flat-earth-how-did-youtube-help-spread-a-conspiracy-theory |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Twitter|Twitter]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Heigl|first1=Alex|url=http://people.com/celebrity/flat-earth-celebrities-world-not-round/|title=The Short List of Famous People Who Think the Earth Is Flat (Yes, Really)|website=People|date=2017-02-20|accessdate=2020-05-08|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412150355/https://people.com/celebrity/flat-earth-celebrities-world-not-round/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[Facebook|Facebook]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Abbott|first1=Erica|title=Mark Zuckerberg Banning All Flat Earth Groups from Facebook Is A Hoax|url=http://www.business2community.com/facebook/mark-zuckerberg-banning-flat-earth-groups-facebook-hoax-01890594#WRFxzo1QOD9xCO2F.97|website=Business2community.com|publisher=Business2community|accessdate=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819231354/http://www.business2community.com/facebook/mark-zuckerberg-banning-flat-earth-groups-facebook-hoax-01890594#WRFxzo1QOD9xCO2F.97|archive-date=2017-08-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这样的大型、知名的社交媒体很容易将正确信息传播扩散于大众之中，但同时，也很容易散播错误的信息并于此之上建立强有力的支撑，地平说猜想正是在这种环境之下得到了快速发展<ref name="Ambrose" /><ref name="Dure" /><ref>{{cite news|last1=Herreria|first1=Carla|title=Neil deGrasse Tyson Cites Celebrity Flat-Earthers To Make A Point About Politics|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/neil-degrasse-tyson-flat-earth-pop-stars-flawed_us_58faa373e4b06b9cb91719ad|newspaper=Huffington Post|accessdate=2017-08-19|date=2017-04-22|archive-date=2019-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208063934/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/neil-degrasse-tyson-flat-earth-pop-stars-flawed_us_58faa373e4b06b9cb91719ad|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

YouTube因为传播错误信息与阴谋论而长期遭受着大量来自社会的指责与批评。2019年，Youtube聲明將對包括地平说在内的阴谋论相关的影片降权<ref name="YouTubeCrackdown">{{cite news |title=YouTube says it will crack down on recommending conspiracy videos |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/01/25/tech/youtube-conspiracy-video-recommendations/index.html |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=CNN |archive-date=2020-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529192913/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/01/25/tech/youtube-conspiracy-video-recommendations/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="YouTube converted people" /><ref name="Picheta">{{cite news |last1=CNN |first1=Rob Picheta |title=The flat earth conspiracy is spreading around the globe. Does it hide a darker core? |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/11/16/us/flat-earth-conference-conspiracy-theories-scli-intl/index.html |accessdate=2019-11-17 |work=CNN |archive-date=2020-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200520144747/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/11/16/us/flat-earth-conference-conspiracy-theories-scli-intl/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 作为阴谋论出现 ===
地平说协会的成员和其他地平说支持者认为[[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]]与其他的政府机构联合起来欺骗了大众<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.livescience.com/24310-flat-earth-belief.html|title=Are Flat-Earthers Being Serious?|last=Wolchover|first=Natalie|last2=May 30|first2=Live Science Staff {{!}}|website=Live Science|access-date=2019-01-17|last3=ET|first3=2017 10:24am|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119121455/https://www.livescience.com/24310-flat-earth-belief.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们的主要论据是NASA正在保护围绕地球的南极冰墙<ref name=":1" />。地平说支持者认为NASA[[修飾照片|篡改]]了他们的[[卫星影像|卫星影像]]，因为他们观察发现海洋的颜色因图像的不同而变化，并且各大洲似乎位于与实际不同的地方<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/global/2018/may/27/is-the-earth-pancake-flat-among-the-flat-earthers-conspiracy-theories-fake-news|title=Is the Earth flat? Meet the people questioning science|last=Moshakis|first=Alex|date=2018-05-27|work=The Observer|access-date=2019-01-17|language=en-GB|issn=0029-7712|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119121452/https://www.theguardian.com/global/2018/may/27/is-the-earth-pancake-flat-among-the-flat-earthers-conspiracy-theories-fake-news|dead-url=no}}</ref>。地平说支持者认为政府屏蔽了真相，只有少部分聪明人才能看出真相<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.newyorker.com/science/elements/looking-for-life-on-a-flat-earth|title=Looking for Life on a Flat Earth|last=Burdick|first=Alan|date=2018-05-30|access-date=2019-01-17|language=en|issn=0028-792X|archive-date=2019-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190117001429/https://www.newyorker.com/science/elements/looking-for-life-on-a-flat-earth|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

